62
00:04:53,620 --> 00:04:54,339
Open the door.

63
00:04:55,379 --> 00:04:56,000
Don't hide.

64
00:04:56,220 --> 00:04:56,759
Open the door!

65
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:57,439
Open the door!

66
00:04:59,660 --> 00:05:00,560
Open the door!

67
00:05:01,199 --> 00:05:02,100
