Mom, don't go.

76
00:05:45,019 --> 00:05:45,899
Mom, don't go.

77
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,660
Mom.

78
00:05:57,180 --> 00:05:57,759
Mom.

79
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,079
