130
00:08:26,259 --> 00:08:27,519
The bus is about to leave.

131
00:08:27,519 --> 00:08:28,779
Pack up quickly.

132
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:29,720
We can't stay

133
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,800
