159
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,740
Have you considered

160
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:23,120
selling the house to a third party?

161
00:09:23,340 --> 00:09:24,059
No way.

162
00:09:26,019 --> 00:09:27,039
Yi,

163
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,360
