186
00:09:56,179 --> 00:09:57,159
What should Miao Jing do?

187
00:10:12,500 --> 00:10:13,360
Jing, come on.

188
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,340
Get in the car.

189
00:10:14,700 --> 00:10:15,240
Wait,

190
00:10:15,340 --> 00:10:16,659
