191
00:10:16,980 --> 00:10:18,259
Get in the car, we'll talk later.

192
00:10:18,259 --> 00:10:18,779
There's no time left.

193
00:10:18,779 --> 00:10:19,379
How can I

194
00:10:19,379 --> 00:10:20,299
