220
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:45,519
No, no, no!

221
00:10:45,519 --> 00:10:46,360
Who are you?

222
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,000
It's a misunderstanding!

223
00:10:47,259 --> 00:10:47,679
Jingjing!

224
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:48,000
It's a misunderstanding!

225
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:48,639
Tell them

226
00:10:48,740 --> 00:10:49,820
