235
00:11:00,580 --> 00:11:01,220
Go, go.

236
00:11:03,559 --> 00:11:04,100
Miao Jing.

237
00:11:13,399 --> 00:11:14,340
Go inside.

238
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:14,980
Go.

239
00:11:22,379 --> 00:11:23,179
[The direction of LinGang.]

240
00:11:23,379 --> 00:11:24,100
