242
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:25,779
[please line up.]

243
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:43,200
[Don't crowd.]

244
00:11:43,519 --> 00:11:44,639
[Line up.]

245
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,659
Give me your phone.

246
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:56,559
