252
00:12:02,259 --> 00:12:03,159
Give me your phone.

253
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:08,220
[Everyone, move forward.]

254
00:12:08,220 --> 00:12:09,039
[Come and line up.]

255
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:09,980
