689
00:30:52,220 --> 00:30:53,059
Okay, okay.

690
00:30:54,220 --> 00:30:54,859
Okay.

691
00:30:55,180 --> 00:30:56,359
That's it for today.

692
00:30:56,579 --> 00:30:57,039
