867
00:39:15,559 --> 00:39:16,179
You sit down too.

868
00:39:16,179 --> 00:39:16,820
What are you talking about?

869
00:39:16,820 --> 00:39:17,559
You just...

870
00:39:17,900 --> 00:39:18,500
You said...

871
00:39:19,380 --> 00:39:20,039
