875
00:39:24,519 --> 00:39:25,179
No, officer.

876
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:25,880
Look at this.

877
00:39:25,880 --> 00:39:26,739
She is the daughter

878
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:27,760
